---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Form Pengaduan - PPID SMKN 14 Jakarta">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Form Pengaduan</h1>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">Penting!</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-700 text-sm">
              Pengaduan yang Anda sampaikan akan kami proses sesuai dengan prosedur yang berlaku.
              Pastikan informasi yang Anda berikan benar dan dapat dipertanggungjawabkan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Data Pelapor -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">A. Data Pelapor</h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="nama" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Nama Lengkap *</label>
                <input type="text" id="nama" name="nama" required
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="nik" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">NIK/KTP *</label>
                <input type="text" id="nik" name="nik" required
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="alamat" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Alamat Lengkap *</label>
                <textarea id="alamat" name="alamat" rows="3" required
                         class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="pekerjaan" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Pekerjaan</label>
                <input type="text" id="pekerjaan" name="pekerjaan"
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="telepon" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Nomor Telepon *</label>
                <input type="tel" id="telepon" name="telepon" required
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Email *</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pengaduan -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">B. Isi Pengaduan</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label for="jenis_pengaduan" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Jenis Pengaduan *</label>
                <select id="jenis_pengaduan" name="jenis_pengaduan" required
                        class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                  <option value="">-- Pilih Jenis Pengaduan --</option>
                  <option value="pelayanan">Pelayanan PPID</option>
                  <option value="informasi">Informasi yang Diberikan</option>
                  <option value="prosedur">Prosedur Permohonan</option>
                  <option value="petugas">Sikap Petugas</option>
                  <option value="website">Website/Teknis</option>
                  <option value="lainnya">Lainnya</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="subjek_pengaduan" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Subjek Pengaduan *</label>
                <input type="text" id="subjek_pengaduan" name="subjek_pengaduan" required
                       placeholder="Ringkasan singkat pengaduan Anda"
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="kronologi" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Kronologi Kejadian *</label>
                <textarea id="kronologi" name="kronologi" rows="5" required
                         placeholder="Jelaskan secara detail kronologi kejadian yang Anda alami..."
                         class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="dampak" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Dampak yang Dirasakan</label>
                <textarea id="dampak" name="dampak" rows="3"
                         placeholder="Jelaskan dampak atau kerugian yang Anda alami akibat kejadian ini..."
                         class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="harapan" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Harapan Penyelesaian *</label>
                <textarea id="harapan" name="harapan" rows="3" required
                         placeholder="Jelaskan harapan Anda terhadap penyelesaian pengaduan ini..."
                         class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Bukti Pendukung -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">C. Bukti Pendukung</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Upload Bukti (Foto, Dokumen, dll)</label>
                <input type="file" id="bukti_pendukung" name="bukti_pendukung" multiple
                       accept=".jpg,.jpeg,.png,.pdf,.doc,.docx"
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Format: JPG, PNG, PDF, DOC. Maksimal 5MB per file.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="saksi" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Nama Saksi (Jika Ada)</label>
                <input type="text" id="saksi" name="saksi"
                       placeholder="Nama saksi yang mengetahui kejadian"
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="kontak_saksi" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Kontak Saksi</label>
                <input type="text" id="kontak_saksi" name="kontak_saksi"
                       placeholder="Nomor telepon atau email saksi"
                       class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Kesediaan -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">D. Kesediaan untuk Diwawancarai</h2>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label class="flex items-center">
                <input type="radio" name="kesediaan_wawancara" value="ya" class="mr-2">
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Ya, saya bersedia diwawancarai untuk klarifikasi lebih lanjut</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center">
                <input type="radio" name="kesediaan_wawancara" value="tidak" class="mr-2">
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Tidak, saya tidak bersedia diwawancarai</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pernyataan -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">E. Pernyataan</h2>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-md">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
                Saya menyatakan bahwa informasi yang disampaikan dalam pengaduan ini adalah benar dan dapat dipertanggungjawabkan.
                Saya bersedia untuk memberikan klarifikasi lebih lanjut jika diperlukan.
              </p>
              <label class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" name="pernyataan" required class="mr-2">
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Saya setuju dengan pernyataan di atas *</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Buttons -->
          <div class="flex justify-between pt-6">
            <button type="reset"
                    class="bg-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors duration-200">
              Reset Form
            </button>
            <button type="submit"
                    class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors duration-200">
              Kirim Pengaduan
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Proses Pengaduan:</h3>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-blue-700 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>Pengaduan akan diverifikasi dalam waktu 3 hari kerja</li>
          <li>Jika memenuhi syarat, pengaduan akan ditindaklanjuti</li>
          <li>Proses investigasi maksimal 14 hari kerja</li>
          <li>Hasil akan disampaikan melalui email/telepon yang terdaftar</li>
          <li>Kerahasiaan pelapor akan dijamin sesuai ketentuan</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>